# 月夜 · Supabase Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create a free project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Go to: Settings → API
# 3. Copy your Project URL and anon/public key below
# 4. Run the SQL in supabase-setup.sql in your Supabase SQL editor
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON=your-anon-key-here

# For Vercel deployment, add these same values in:
# Vercel dashboard → your project → Settings → Environment Variables
